3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper involves learning deep depth features and applying a multi-task training scheme, which are both related to machine learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of depth information for improving computer vision tasks can be seen as a subfield of artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper involves processing and analyzing visual data, which falls under the scope of multimedia research.
